                    <paragraph align="center">
                        釋<index type="이름">靈潤</index>
                        , 俗姓<index type="이름">梁</index>, <index type="지명">河東</index>
                        <index type="지명">虞鄕</index>人也, 家世衣冠鄕閭望族. …… <index type="연호">大業</index>十年<emph align="center" space="one" type="bold">(614)</emph>, 被召入鴻臚, 敎授<index type="국명">三韓</index>, 幷在本寺翻新經本, 並宗轄有承不虧風采. </paragraph>
